1.python版本
  首先需要安装zlib
  python -V查看python版本，确保python为python27
  wget http://python.org/ftp/python/2.7/Python-2.7.tar.bz2
  tar -jxvf Python-2.7.tar.bz2
  cd Python-2.7
  ./configure
  make all
  sudo make install
  make clean
  make distclean
  /usr/local/bin/python2.7 -V

  建立软链接指向默认python2.7
  #mv /usr/bin/python /usr/bin/python2.6
  #ln -s /usr/local/bin/python2.7 /usr/bin/python
  输入python -V检查
  
  更改python版本后，可能会导致yum不可使用，解决办法如下：	
  #修改yum文件
  vi /usr/bin/yum
  将文件头部的
  #!/usr/bin/python
  改为如下内容	
  #!/usr/bin/python2.6

2.esay_insatll
  先安装distribute-0.6.10
  安装setuptools-7.0

3.相关库的安装
  pip install python-dateutil flup Django==1.6 SQLAlchemy==0.9.4 django-localeurl python-memcached  xlrd tornado pyparsing gearman
  wget  http://initd.org/psycopg/tarballs/PSYCOPG-2-5/psycopg2-2.5.4.tar.gz
  tar xf psycopg2-2.5.4.tar.gz
  cd psycopg2-2.5.4
  yum install -y postgresql-devel*
  python setup.py build
  sudo python setup.py install

  sudo yum install gcc-gfortran libgfortran blas-devvel blas lapack lapack-devel gcc-c++ libuuid-devel gperf boost-devel memcached memcached-devel
  pip install numpy scipy matplotlib scikit-learn

  sudo /etc/rc.d/init.d/postgresql restart

4.数据库配置
  sudo -u postgres psql
  postgres=#  ALTER USER postgres WITH PASSWORD 'pku123';
  create user tao with password 'pku123'; #密码设置为local_settings.py配置的值
  alter role tao with superuser;
  create database gflux；
  

  vi /var/lib/pgsql/data/pg_hba.conf改成md5方式，否则无法登录数据库，service postgresql restart重启

5.初始化
  python manage.py syncdb
  python manage.py init_gflux_dev_env
  python manage.py init_fuel_type_relation
  python manage.py init_loc_site_fueltype_datehours

6.设置定时任务执行网感指数，开启相应的gearman
  #gearmand -d
  
  gearmand --log-file gearmand.log --listen 127.0.0.1 --port=4730 --verbose=INFO &


  
  
  
